# Commit & PR Standards

- Commit message and PR must link the ADEF change doc.
- Include summary of tests, gate results, and risk/rollback notes.
- No merge until all CI checks pass.

Checklist:
- [ ] Change doc created and linked
- [ ] Gates pass locally (lint, mypy, verify, gates)
- [ ] CI green
- [ ] Secrets not in code/logs

